---
title: Steaks and Bacon-Balsamic Sauce with Mustardy Brussels Sprouts and Herbed Potatoes
description: Thinking about having company over? This dish is made to impress! A plate of heavenly bacon-balsamic sauce draped over tender steak is a sure-fire dinner hit with its savoury-sweet notes! Brussels sprouts tossed in mustard and buttery herbed potatoes complete this gorgeous meal.
